---
title: Pesto Veggie Fritters and Caprese Style Salad with Pine Nuts and Herby Potatoes
description: Making vegetable fritters is easier than you think! Flavoured with pesto, these onion and carrot fritters are paired with herby roast potatoes and a classic Caprese style salad for a colourful dinner.
